{"tid":1326601,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣片] 一齊走下去  721見","createTime":"2019-07-17T09:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T09:16:37.000Z","uid":169855,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6f481eb9f2dd4487dcdc0e2e8c8cfbb271314678","tid":1326601,"uid":169855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:38:25.000Z","msg":"整咗條片 提下大家點解721要上街<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JNBf5vX8o_w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJNBf5vX8o_w&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5auUzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=3ede10a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JNBf5vX8o_w</a><br />\n<br />\n大家背負既係烈士們既遺願<br />\n721 大家代佢地一齊走下去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一個都不能少<br />\n不流血，不受傷，不被捕<br />\n不分化，不篤灰，不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7ff98822b189c30ecddb3a8cb7702c8ac8141e2d","tid":1326601,"uid":169855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:39:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2d2bd335f8dbc0dab9d0de3a8b65049c71ad1605","tid":1326601,"uid":131040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:40:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b991ff8efb99f6ab974af3a9ae72c718b463e13f","tid":1326601,"uid":277666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:40:39.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n感激香港仲有你地"},{"pid":"e79f2db0acdc9074b10318d462d0a8e7d87fb06c","tid":1326601,"uid":256914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:42:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2ad1dcc74821a35f6cb3b8ca6c0967fa543889f4","tid":1326601,"uid":138774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:43:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"50291c4595e1f7306f03eb087b4ff8135e5a4913","tid":1326601,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi